
<div class="container">
	<div class ="list-top-back">
		<%= link_to "", root_path, class: "glyphicon glyphicon-home"%>
		<span  class="text-capitalize"><%= @product.name %></span>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="list-element">
			<div class="detailed-content-top">
				<div class="col-md-5">
					<%= image_tag(@product.images_url(:thumbnail), alt: "images", id: "zoom_02", data: { zoom_image: @product.images_url})%>
					<script>
					    $('#zoom_02').elevateZoom({
						    zoomType: "inner",
							cursor: "crosshair",
					    }); 
					</script>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-4">
					<p><%= @product.name %></p>
					<dl>
						<dt>Description</dt>
						<dd><%=@product.description %></dd>
					</dl>
					<div class="detailed-button">
  						<a class="btn btn-default" href="https://twitter.com" role="button">Tweet</a>
  						<a class="btn btn-default" href="https://facebook.com" role="button">Share</a>
  						<a class="btn btn-default" href="https://google.com" role="button">Google+</a>
  						<a class="btn btn-default" href="https://google.com" role="button">Printerest</a>
					</div>
					<div class="detailed-write">
						<a href="@"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil" aria-hidden="true"></span>	Write a review</a>
					</div>
					<div class="detailed-sent-print">
						<a href="@"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope" aria-hidden="true"></span> Sent to a friend</a>
						<br/>
						<a href="@"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-print" aria-hidden="true"></span> Print</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-3">
					<div class="detailed-right">
						<%= form_for @order_item, remote: true do |f| %>
							<div class="detailed-right-box">
								<p><%= number_to_currency @product.price %></p>
							</div>
							<div class="detailed-right-box">
								<label>Quantity</label>
								<%= f.number_field :quantity, value: 1, class: "form-control", min: 1 %>
								<%= f.hidden_field :product_id, value: @product.id %>
	 					 	</div>
	 					 	<div class="detailed-right-box">
	 					 		<div class="row">
		 					 		<div class="col-md-12">
			 					 		<%= f.submit "Add to Cart", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
			 					 	</div>
			 					 	<div class="col-md-12">
			 					 		<a href="#"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart-empty"></span> Add to wishlist</a>
			 					 	</div>
		 					 	</div>
		 					</div>
		 					<img src="http://livedemo00.template-help.com/prestashop_52530/modules/productpaymentlogos/img/payment-logo.png"/>
						<% end %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row container">
		<div class="detailed-content-bottom">
			<div class="list-element-left">
				<p>MORE INFO</p>
				<div class="detailed-box-text">
					<span>How many hobbies are there in the world around you? Tastes differ and each of us chooses the activities that reflect his or her interests and bring the pleasant pastime. Most girls like playing dolls, most boys prefer examining construction sets, toy cars and parts of whatever devices they can find. Of course, accidents happen, and sometimes you can notice a little girl in a beautiful dress sitting and rummaging the unusual for her metal devices instead of lullabying her favorite teddy bear.
As you see, tastes differ, but there is one childish hobby that is interesting both for boys and girls, their moms and dads, and it is radio control hobby. This is the very thing that is driving people of all ages, genders and social positions mad. It’s so agitating and exciting, that you forget about everything else when you get your first RC toy and it doesn’t matter what it is. It can be a car, a bike, a plane, a helicopter, or whatever you can imagine. You can spend hours playing with it, examining it and the whole day (or even more) can pass without being noticed.
At our store, you will find the ultimate assortment of things that can become real presents for your radio control hobby. Here you can find whatever cool things you can imagine that will make your hobby even more interesting and captivating.
Stay with us and make your life brighter with more hobbies!</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="list-element-left">
				<p>PRODUCTS IN THE SAME CATEGORY: </p>
				<div class="row products-box">
				<% dem=0
					@products.each do |product|
						if product.category_id == @product.category_id
							dem += 1 %>
						<div class="col-md-2">
							<%= link_to image_tag(product.images_url, alt:"images"), product_path(product) %>
							<div class="products-box-text">
								<%= link_to product.name, product_path(product)%>
							</div>
							<span>$ <%= product.price %></span>
						</div>
					<%	 break if dem == 3
						end
					end %>
				</div>
			</div>	
		</div>
	</div>
</div>